@page "/"

<PageTitle>Djehuti Teacher — Learn at the Speed of AI</PageTitle>

<div class="teacher-hero">
    <span class="teacher-hero-mark">DT</span>
    <h1>Learn at the speed of AI.</h1>
    <p class="teacher-tagline">Djehuti Teacher builds lesson plans, runs classes, and tracks progress — with an AI tutor whose job is comprehension, not answers. Bring your own key, and it works through the problem with you instead of just handing you the solution.</p>

    <div class="teacher-hero-actions">
        <a class="teacher-cta" href="catalog">Browse the catalog</a>
        <a class="teacher-cta teacher-cta-ghost" href="getting-started">How it works</a>
    </div>

    <div class="teacher-hero-grid">
        <div class="teacher-hero-card">
            <h2>Built to teach, not to answer</h2>
            <p>The AI is instructed to scaffold understanding — hints, guiding questions, worked-through reasoning — not hand over a finished answer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="teacher-hero-card">
            <h2>Real math, live</h2>
            <p>Interactive computation and plotting built on the same engine as DjeLab — worked examples run and graph in the browser, not as static images.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="teacher-hero-card">
            <h2>Anyone can teach</h2>
            <p>Build a lesson plan on any subject, publish it to the catalog, and track how your students are doing as they work through it.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
